# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok indonesia warned monday that its most volatile volcano could erupt at any time , prompting calls for the evacuation of thousands of villagers living on the mountain 's slopes .
# ::alignments
(w / warn-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Indonesia"))
      :ARG1 (p / possible-01
            :ARG1 (e / erupt-01
                  :ARG1 (v / volcano
                        :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                              :ARG2 (v2 / volatile)
                              :ARG3 (m / most)
                              :ARG5 c))
                  :time (a / any)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (m2 / monday))
      :ARG0-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG1 (c3 / call-03
                  :ARG1 (e2 / evacuate-01
                        :ARG2 (v3 / villager
                              :quant (m3 / multiple
                                    :op1 1000)
                              :ARG0-of (l / live-01
                                    :location (s / slope
                                          :poss (m4 / mountain))))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok national security chief alexander lebed arrived at a russian base near the chechen capital grozny wednesday on a new peace mission to prevent a russian all-out assault on rebels in the city , interfax news agency reported .
# ::alignments
(r / report-01
      :ARG0 (a / agency
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Interpol")
            :mod (n2 / news))
      :ARG1 (a2 / arrive-01
            :ARG1 (p / person
                  :name (n3 / name
                        :op1 "Alexander"
                        :op2 "Lebed")
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG2 (c / chief
                              :topic (s / security
                                    :mod (n4 / nation)))))
            :ARG4 (b / base
                  :mod (c2 / country
                        :name (n5 / name
                              :op1 "Russia"))
                  :ARG1-of (n6 / near-02
                        :ARG2 (c3 / city
                              :name (n7 / name
                                    :op1 "Grozny")
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG1 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n8 / name
                                                :op1 "Chechnya"))
                                    :ARG2 (c5 / capital)))))
            :time (w / wednesday)
            :purpose (m / mission-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (p2 / prevent-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (a3 / assault-01
                              :ARG0 c2
                              :ARG1 (p3 / person
                                    :ARG0-of (r2 / rebel-01))
                              :mod (a4 / all-out)
                              :location c3))
                  :mod (p4 / peace)
                  :ARG1-of (n9 / new-01))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok larry kent , who as the first president of nfl properties , the licensing and marketing arm of the national football league , lived to see it grow from gross revenue of $ ##,### in #### to $ # billion in #### , died july ## in his home in palm beach , fla. .

      :ARG1 (p / person

                  :op1 "Larry"
                  :op2 "Kent")

                              :op1 "Nfl"
                              :op2 "Property")

                              :ARG1 (a / arm
                                    :ARG0-of (l / license-01)
                                    :ARG0-of (m / market-01)
                                    :part-of (l2 / league
                                          :mod (f / football)
                                          :mod (n3 / nation))))
                        :ARG2 (p2 / president
                              :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                                    :value 1)))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :month 7)
      :location (h3 / home
            :location (b / beach
                  :name (n4 / name
                        :op1 "Pal palm"))
            :poss p)
      :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
            :ARG0 (s / see-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (g / grow-01
                        :ARG1 c
                        :ARG3 (r / revenue
                              :ARG1-of (g2 / gross-03)
                              :mod (m2 / monetary-quantity
                                    :quant 1000000000
                                    :unit (d3 / dollar)
                                    :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                                          :ARG2 r)))
                        :ARG4 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000000
                              :unit (d4 / dollar)
                              :ARG1-of ii
                              :ARG2 r)))))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a finnish officer on wednesday assumed command of a brigade of nato-led peacekeepers in kosovo , marking the first time a non-nato officer took command of an alliance unit .
# ::alignments
(a / assume-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (o / officer))
            :mod (c / country
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Finland")))
      :ARG1 (c2 / command-02
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (b / brigade
                  :consist-of (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of (k / keep-01
                              :ARG1 (p3 / peace))
                        :ARG1-of (l / lead-02
                              :ARG0 (e / ethnic-group
                                    :polarity -
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Nato"))))
                  :location (c3 / city
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Kosovo"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (w / wednesday))
      :ARG0-of (m / mark-01
            :ARG1 (t / take-01
                  :ARG0 (p4 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG2 (o2 / officer))
                        :mod e)
                  :ARG1 (c4 / command-02
                        :ARG0 p4
                        :ARG1 (u / unit
                              :ARG0-of (a2 / ally-01))
                        :ord (o3 / ordinal-entity
                              :value 1)))))

            :ARG2 (e2 / evade-01

                        :op1 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 1000000

# ::id 6 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "West")))

            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (s / situation
                  :time (c / current)
                  :location (c2 / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "Iran")))
            :manner (t2 / term
                  :mod (a / alarmist))
            :ARG0-of (s2 / suggest-01
                  :ARG1 (a2 / and
                        :op1 (n3 / near-02
                              :ARG1 (p2 / person)
                              :ARG2 (r2 / revolt-01
                                    :ARG0 p2))
                        :op2 (f / face-01
                              :ARG0 (r3 / regime)
                              :ARG1 (c3 / collapse-01
                                    :ARG1 r3))
                        :op3 (p3 / prone-01
                              :ARG1 c2
                              :ARG2 (u / upheaval
                                    :mod (p4 / politics)))))))

(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (g / government-organization
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Pentagon"))
      :ARG1 (g2 / go-01
            :ARG1 (a / and
                  :op1 (w / warship)
                  :op2 (p / plane)
                  :mod (c / country
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "U.S.")))
            :ARG4 (w2 / water
                  :location (s2 / south
                        :part-of c
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Korea"))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :time (a2 / after
            :op1 (e / exchange-01
                  :ARG0 (r / republic
                        :poss (p2 / people
                              :mod (d2 / democracy)))
                  :ARG1 (f / fire)
                  :ARG2 (r2 / republic
                        :poss c)
                  :location (s3 / sea
                        :ARG1-of (y / yellow-02))
                  :time (w3 / week
                        :mod (t2 / this)))))
